 robust indoor localization with unobtrusive\ninfrastructure, with a computational efficiency suitable for real-time\nprocessing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Aug 2017 16:21:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-08"}
