dence of baryon number violation is found, and an upper limit at\nthe 95% confidence level is set on the oscillation rate of $\\omega < 0.08$\nps$^{-1}$, where $\\omega$ is the associated angular frequency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 19 Aug 2017 05:44:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 4 Nov 2017 11:53:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-07"}
